      "content": "wait r u sure? i get cramps like this every month and they can get really sharp. i dont really want to go to the er at 2am if it's just gas or something. if i take a couple of ibuprofen and maybe some paracetamol too, wouldn't that just help the inflammation if it is something minor? i really just need to get some sleep.",
